<i>noun</i>: 변절 [변ː절], 배신 [배ː신], 배반 [배ː반], 모반 [모반] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>변절 [변ː절]</dt><br>
<dd>betrayal; treachery</dd><br>
<dd>믿음이나 의지, 도리를 지키지 않고 바꿈.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of abandoning one's belief, will or duty, and taking on an opposing belief, will or duty.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>배신 [배ː신]</dt><br>
<dd>betrayal; treachery</dd><br>
<dd>상대방의 믿음과 의리를 저버림.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of betraying the other side's trust and fidelity.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>배반 [배ː반]</dt><br>
<dd>betrayal; treachery</dd><br>
<dd>사람들과의 관계에서 지켜야 할 믿음과 의리에 어긋나게 행동함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act or behavior against trust and loyalty that one is expected to maintain in a relationship.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>모반 [모반]</dt><br>
<dd>1. conspiracy; betrayal</dd><br>
<dd>배반을 꾀함.</dd><br>
<dd>The attempt of betrayal.</dd><br>
<dd>2. treason; rebellion</dd><br>
<dd>국가나 임금을 무너뜨리려고 꾀함.</dd><br>
<dd>An uprising against the government or sovereign.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>